Api's with name(relative urls)

Add blog:
url - /app1/blog/
method - post
sample request payload(json) -
{
	"title": "test blog",
	"content": "para1\n\npara2\n\npara3"
}
sample response -
{
    "status": "Request Successful.",
    "msg": "Blog created.",
    "blog_id": 26
}

Paginated blogs(blog list):
url - /app1/blogs/ or /app1/blogs/<page_number>
method - get
request payload - not needed
sample response -
{
    "status": "",
    "msg": "",
    "blogs": {
        "15": [<blog_id>
            [
                [
                    "para1",<paragraph_text>
                    12<paragraph_id>
                ]
            ],
            [
                [
                    "para2",
                    13
                ]
            ],
            [
                [
                    "para3",
                    14
                ]
            ]
        ],
        "17": [
            [
                [
                    "para1",
                    18
                ]
            ],
            [
                [
                    "para2",
                    19
                ]
            ],
            [
                [
                    "para3",
                    20
                ]
            ]
        ],
    },
    "current_page": 1,
    "total_pages": 3
}

Blog details:
url - /app1/blog/<blog_id>/
method - post
sample request payload - not needed.
sample response -
{
    "status": "",
    "msg": "",
    "blog_details": {
        "content": [
            [
                [
                    "para1",<paragraph_text>
                    9<paragraph_id>
                ],
                [<comments_array(orderd by date)>
                    "salty comments again",
                    "salty comments"
                ]
            ],
            [
                [
                    "para2",
                    10
                ],
                []
            ],
            [
                [
                    "para3",
                    11
                ],
                []
            ]
        ],
        "title": "test blog"
    }
}

Add comments:
url - /app1/blog/paragraph/<paragraph_id>/comment/
method - post
sample request payload(json) -
{
	"blog_id": "14",
	"comment_text": "salty comment"
}
sample response -
{
    "status": "Request successfull.",
    "msg": "Comment added.",
    "comment_id": 3
}

